Charles Vane (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Vane_(actor) 0 Charles Vane (born William George Yarrow; 2 January 1860 – 14 April 1943) was a British stage and film actor. Vane appeared in more than fifty films during the silent era including the lead in When It Was Dark (1919).
